      "turn_id": "dialogue_00145_turn_03",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_1",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_2"
    },
    {
      "text": "I would be interested in firewood.  Can I ask you, what are your primary concerns on this trip?",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        }
      },
      "id": "mturk_agent_2",
      "turn_index": 4,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00145_turn_04",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_2",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_1"
    },
    {
      "text": "My primary concerns are staying hydrated, I have been feeling sick and throwing up from being so high up in the mountains. ",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        }
      },
      "id": "mturk_agent_1",
      "turn_index": 5,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00145_turn_05",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_1",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_2"
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh, so sorry to hear that.  I can understand why water would be important to you.  I am worried about being too cold at night. My sleeping bag is not rated well for cold weather (I packed the wring one).",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        }
      },
      "id": "mturk_agent_2",
      "turn_index": 6,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00145_turn_06",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_2",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_1"
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh I understand that for sure. I am not used to the cold weather either which is not helping. Would you be interested in a trade for water in exchange for firewood? ",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        }
      },
      "id": "mturk_agent_1",
      "turn_index": 7,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00145_turn_07",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_1",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_2"
    },
    {
      "text": "Well, I am worried about staying hydrated as well.",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
